1
00:00:02,005 --> 00:00:04,063
前情提要...
Previously on Lost...

2
00:00:04,064 --> 00:00:07,042
你可以回去了
You can go back to your camp.

3
00:00:07,043 --> 00:00:08,071
那我的朋友呢?
What about my friends?

4
00:00:08,072 --> 00:00:11,025
你要做的是回去告诉你们的人
Your job is to tell the rest of your people

5
00:00:11,026 --> 00:00:13,038
永远不要来找我们
they can never come here.

6
00:00:13,039 --> 00:00:18,006
安息吧 Eko先生
Rest in peace, Mr.Eko.

7
00:00:18,007 --> 00:00:21,012
谢谢你帮我找到...
And thank you for helping me find my...

8
00:00:21,013 --> 00:00:25,090
抬起你的头向北看 John

9
00:00:25,091 --> 00:00:27,076
我不在乎Jack怎么说
I don't care what Jack said.

10
00:00:27,077 --> 00:00:29,020
我们要把他找回来
They've got him, and we have to get him back.

11
00:00:29,021 --> 00:00:30,072
这是我欠他的
I owe him that.

12
00:00:30,073 --> 00:00:33,084
珍珠站是一个监控站
The pearl is a monitoring station

13
00:00:33,085 --> 00:00:37,068
此舱用于监视和观察
where the activities of participants in the Dharma initiative projects

14
00:00:37,069 --> 00:00:43,027
达摩实验的参与者
can be observed and recorded.

15
00:00:46,077 --> 00:00:51,095
他一定在等待我们
I guess he'll be expecting us.

16
00:01:05,044 --> 00:01:07,020
乒乓台?
Ping-Pong table?

17
00:01:07,021 --> 00:01:08,098
这东西从哪儿弄来的?
Where the hell did that come from?

18
00:01:08,099 --> 00:01:11,080
Jin在我们找木柴的时候找到的
Jin found it when he was out looking for firewood.

19
00:01:11,081 --> 00:01:14,062
我们做了桌子腿和球拍
We made legs for it and paddles.

20
00:01:14,063 --> 00:01:16,032
我们需要的是球
Now all we need is a ball.

21
00:01:16,033 --> 00:01:17,097
是找到的?
Found it?

22
00:01:17,098 --> 00:01:20,097
一定是舱里爆炸后飞出来的
Must have landed in the jungle when the hatch exploded.

23
00:01:20,098 --> 00:01:22,040
我以为舱里只是倒塌了
I thought the hatch collapsed.

24
00:01:22,041 --> 00:01:24,041
我只知道天空变成了紫色
Look, dude, all I know is the sky turned purple.

25
00:01:24,042 --> 00:01:28,082
从那以后 我就不再问问题了 我要开始新的生活
After that, I don't ask questions, just make myself a salad and move on.

26
00:01:28,083 --> 00:01:31,010
是啊 那还真管用
Yeah, I can see that's working for you.

27
00:01:31,011 --> 00:01:34,002
你看见kate了吗?
You seen Kate around?

28
00:01:34,003 --> 00:01:38,070
她还没回来吗?
she's not back yet?

29
00:01:38,071 --> 00:01:41,000
有什么东西能当球打吗?
You guys find anything we can use for a ball?

30
00:01:41,001 --> 00:01:43,078
没有
No

31
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:45,086
那是我的"枪支与军火"
Hey, that's my "Guns & Ammo."

32
00:01:45,087 --> 00:01:47,016
怎么会在你手里?
Where the hell did you get it?

33
00:01:47,017 --> 00:01:49,034
我在杂志堆里找到的
It was in the magazine stack.

34
00:01:49,035 --> 00:01:51,072
现在我们资源共享了
We share things now.

35
00:01:51,073 --> 00:01:54,081
听着Zorro 这是我的东西...
Listen, Zorro, it was in my stuff...

36
00:01:54,082 --> 00:01:56,045
当你们以为我死了的时候
Stuff you decided to have a little party with

37
00:01:56,046 --> 00:01:57,095
你们就用我的东西开派对了?
while you thought I was dead.

38
00:01:57,096 --> 00:02:04,046
听着 Hillbilly 如果你想要的话 就拿去吧
Listen, Hillbilly, if you want it that bad, take it.

39
00:02:04,047 --> 00:02:09,028
自己留着吧
Just keep it.

40
00:02:23,036 --> 00:02:27,082
我们得吃东西了
We need to eat.

41
00:02:27,083 --> 00:02:32,077
我们的方向对吗?
Are we still on course?

42
00:02:35,089 --> 00:02:39,065
我们依然朝着北方3-0-5方向前进
We're still heading north on a bearing of 3-0-5.

43
00:02:39,066 --> 00:02:40,060
是的
Yes.

44
00:02:40,061 --> 00:02:42,028
我感到你缺乏信心
I'm sensing a lack of confidence.

45
00:02:42,029 --> 00:02:43,096
我们跟着那棍子上的雕刻
We've been walking for two days

46
00:02:43,097 --> 00:02:47,073
已经走了两天了
following a compass bearing provided by the carvings on a stick.

47
00:02:47,074 --> 00:02:48,057
那么?
And?

48
00:02:48,058 --> 00:02:51,049
你真的认为 这会帮助我们找到"the others"的营地吗?
You really think we're just going to chance upon where the others are?

49
00:02:51,050 --> 00:02:53,057
我不知道我们还会遇到什么
I don't know what we're gonna chance on

50
00:02:53,058 --> 00:03:00,021
但这是我们唯一的方向
but my bearing is the only bearing we got.

51
00:03:01,038 --> 00:03:03,052
我要去找些水果 然后
I'm going to find some fruit,and then,

52
00:03:03,053 --> 00:03:10,038
John 我们要好好谈谈下一步的行动了
John, we're going to have a rational conversation regarding our next move.

