住手
Stop right there.

364
00:30:30,007 --> 00:30:36,048
把枪放下...快点
Put the gun on the ground... now.

365
00:30:45,063 --> 00:30:46,099
你在干什么?
What are you doing?

366
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:48,084
就是她
It's her.

367
00:30:48,085 --> 00:30:50,018
她在那儿!
She was there!

368
00:30:50,019 --> 00:30:51,028
那个码头
She was at the dock.

369
00:30:51,029 --> 00:30:53,055
我们被绑架的时候她在场
She was there when we were kidnapped.

370
00:30:53,056 --> 00:30:58,067
她知道Jack在哪里
She knows where Jack is.

371
00:31:01,005 --> 00:31:06,018
还有其他人在这里吗?
Are there any more of you here?

372
00:31:11,021 --> 00:31:13,097
把她弄到搂上去
Let's take her upstairs.

373
00:31:13,098 --> 00:31:19,041
John 我们上来了!
Come on. John, we're coming up!

374
00:31:19,042 --> 00:31:20,066
John!

375
00:31:20,067 --> 00:31:24,078
在这边
Out here.

376
00:31:24,079 --> 00:31:29,044
快走
Move.

377
