然后我们各走各的路
Then we all go our separate ways.

380
00:31:38,093 --> 00:31:40,045
别听他的
Don't listen to him.

381
00:31:40,046 --> 00:31:42,044
如果他要杀我 我早死了
If he was gonna kill me, I'd be dead already.

382
00:31:42,045 --> 00:31:43,016
给我闭嘴
Shut your mouth.

383
00:31:43,017 --> 00:31:45,035
-听我说  -Sayid别让她跑了
-Listen to me.  -Sayid, do not let her go.

384
00:31:45,036 --> 00:31:46,061
我现在就能杀了你
I will execute you right here

385
00:31:46,062 --> 00:31:48,000
-他不会的  -别说了
-He's not gonna do it.  -Be quiet.

386
00:31:48,001 --> 00:31:49,023
我是让他还活着的唯一原因
I'm the only thing keeping him alive.

387
00:31:49,084 --> 00:31:51,014
大家冷静点
Calm down, everyone.

388
00:31:51,015 --> 00:31:55,010
-Mikhail!  -Sayid

389
00:31:55,011 --> 00:31:56,019
我来解决 John
I'll handle this John.

390
00:31:56,020 --> 00:31:59,098
John...

391
00:32:02,028 --> 00:32:06,075
别让她和他说话!
Don't let her talk to him!

392
00:32:06,076 --> 00:32:11,099
停下! 干吧 Mikhail!
Just do it, Mikhail!

393
00:32:13,073 --> 00:32:18,000
John!

394
00:32:20,095 --> 00:32:25,064
动手吧!
Finish it!

395
00:32:25,078 --> 00:32:30,051
杀了我吧!
Kill me.

396
00:32:45,038 --> 00:32:47,049
抱歉让你输的很难看
Sorry I beat you so bad, dude.

397
00:32:47,050 --> 00:32:50,038
那你还来和我说什么
Sorry you hustled me, you mean.

398
00:32:50,039 --> 00:32:53,043
我妈妈在地下室有个乒乓桌
My mom had a table in her basement,

399
00:32:53,044 --> 00:32:55,012
我在里面...
and I played a lot at the insti...

400
00:32:55,013 --> 00:33:00,059
待了很长时间
This place I hung out for a while.

401
00:33:00,060 --> 00:33:01,054
那感觉真好
I got kinda good.

402
00:33:01,055 --> 00:33:03,097
你真行啊
Well, hooray for you.

403
00:33:03,098 --> 00:33:05,084
这不是你的作风
Doesn't look like at last slam

404
00:33:05,085 --> 00:33:08,095
输了就输了吧...
caused any long-term damage to your forehead...

405
00:33:08,096 --> 00:33:11,021
你得了3分 总比没分强吧
and you got 3 points, which is better than zero.

406
00:33:11,022 --> 00:33:13,002
你想要做什么?
Something you want?

407
00:33:13,003 --> 00:33:15,094
还给你些东西
Came to give you back some of your stuff,

408
00:33:15,095 --> 00:33:19,084
因为你需要这些
Cause, you know, you're the kind of guy that needs stuff.

409
00:33:19,085 --> 00:33:22,081
你这是安慰我吗?
You a shrink now?

410
00:33:22,082 --> 00:33:27,007
她会没事的 Kate
She'll be okay, dude, Kate

411
00:33:27,008 --> 00:33:30,030
我知道你在担心她 但她和Locke和Sayid在一起
I know you're worried about her, But she's with Locke and Sayid.

412
00:33:30,031 --> 00:33:32,001
她不会有事的
She's gonna be fine.

413
00:33:32,002 --> 00:33:36,015
谢谢你的好意 大块头
Yeah, well, thanks for the pep talk,

414
00:33:36,016 --> 00:33:43,027
是Hurley...或者Hugo
It's Hurley...or Hugo, if you want.

415
00:33:43,072 --> 00:33:48,087
去找个板凳吧 Hugo
Get bent, Hugo.

416
00:33:52,092 --> 00:33:55,055
准备好走了吗 Locke?
You ready to go, Locke?

417
00:33:55,056 --> 00:33:59,013
我一会儿就来
I'll be there in a minute.

418
00:33:59,014 --> 00:34:02,081
如果这个站点已被"敌人"入侵
Has there been an incursion on this station by the hostiles?

419
00:34:02,082 --> 00:34:10,030
请输入7-7
If so, enter 7-7.

420
00:34:11,064 --> 00:34:17,026
Danielle! Danielle!

421
00:34:17,051 --> 00:34:19,059
告诉我
Tell me something.

422
00:34:19,060 --> 00:34:23,001
你曾是达摩的一员吗?
Were you ever a member of the Dharma Initiative,

423
00:34:23,002 --> 00:34:26,000
还是你一开始就在撒谎?
or was everything you said a lie?

424
00:34:26,001 --> 00:34:28,055
我当然是在浪费时间
Of course I'm wasting my breath.

425
00:34:28,056 --> 00:34:32,070
我不是达摩的一员 但其它的都是真的
I was never a member, but everything else I told you was true.

426
00:34:32,071 --> 00:34:34,072
"大清洗"后我来到了这个站点
I moved into the station after the purge.

427
00:34:34,073 --> 00:34:37,076
哪个科考团队会袭击你们呢?
The purge, in which a group of scientists attacked your people?

428
00:34:37,077 --> 00:34:41,099
你相不相信随你便 但这些确实发生了
Believe what you want, but that is what happened.

429
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:44,036
你的朋友..他们死了吗?
Your friends.. did he kill them?

430
00:34:44,037 --> 00:34:45,037
没有
No.

431
00:34:45,038 --> 00:34:48,007
他们正在搜集那个农舍可利用的资源
They're collecting whatever may be useful from the farmhouse

432
00:34:48,008 --> 00:34:50,090
现在有人可以带我们去"The others"那里了
and now we have our ticket to where the others live

433
00:34:50,091 --> 00:34:54,043
我们就能找到Jack和你的女儿
where we'll find your daughter and Jack

434
00:34:54,044 --> 00:34:57,063
也许还能找到回家的路
and finally, perhaps, a way home.

435
00:34:57,064 --> 00:35:04,008
我不会带你们去那里的
There is nothing you could do to me that would make me lead you there.

436
00:35:04,009 --> 00:35:10,055
我没有说过让你带路
I didn't say you were our ticket, did I?

437
00:35:15,010 --> 00:35:21,038
这张地图显示与火焰舱连接的各个电缆
This is a map showing electrical and data cabling running from the Flame here,

438
00:35:21,039 --> 00:35:24,076
这个地方叫"the barracks"
to a place called "the Barracks," here.

439
00:35:24,077 --> 00:35:28,054
这是个包括有水和电的住宅区
It's comprised of houses and dormitories with water and power

440
00:35:28,055 --> 00:35:33,002
那些能源足够能提供给整个社区
large enough to accommodate an entire community.

441
00:35:33,003 --> 00:35:37,037
那地方一定很值得拜访
Sounds like a place well worth visiting, don't you think?

442
00:35:37,038 --> 00:35:40,067
你们的警惕会降低
There will come a time when your guard is down

443
00:35:40,068 --> 00:35:47,090
到时我会毫不留情的杀了你们
and when it is, I will not hesitate a moment before killing you.

444
00:35:47,091 --> 00:35:51,091
-你应该知道这点  -他说到点子上了
-You should know this before  -He's making an excellent point.

445
00:35:51,092 --> 00:35:53,040
我们有地图
You have a map.

446
00:35:53,041 --> 00:35:58,048
为什么要让他活着?
Why keep him alive?

447
00:36:22,096 --> 00:36:27,038
我和丈夫到巴黎后
After my husband and I first arrived to Paris

448
00:36:27,039 --> 00:36:32,076
我总是不敢走出公寓一步
I was afraid to ever leave our apartment.

449
00:36:32,077 --> 00:36:36,080
所以我透过窗户看着小巷
So I would stare out the window into the alley

450
00:36:36,081 --> 00:36:40,073
我看见这只猫在寻找剩饭菜
and I would see this cat looking for scraps.

451
00:36:40,074 --> 00:36:46,074
一天 一群孩子把它关在一个箱子里
One day, some children came into the alley and trapped him in a box.

452
00:36:46,075 --> 00:36:55,014
我看着他们往箱子里投入爆竹
I watched them light firecrackers and drop them in the box.

453
00:36:55,015 --> 00:37:01,048
我从三楼就能听到它的嚎叫
I could hear him howl from three stories above.

454
00:37:01,049 --> 00:37:08,016
终于 我有理由走出我的公寓
So finally, I had a reason to leave my apartment.

455
00:37:08,017 --> 00:37:13,001
我救了这只猫 把它带回了家
I rescued this cat, and I brought him home.

456
00:37:13,002 --> 00:37:16,070
当我阅读时 它总在身边
He sits with me when I read.

457
00:37:16,071 --> 00:37:26,011
当我睡觉时 它总是发出咕噜声
He sleeps with me, and he purrs.

458
00:37:26,058 --> 00:37:30,068
但..总有那么些时候
But.. every once in a while

459
00:37:30,069 --> 00:37:37,023
它会咬我 抓我
he will bite me or scratch me.

460
00:37:37,095 --> 00:37:46,030
它这样做是因为它害怕了
He does this because sometimes he forgets that he is safe now.

461
00:37:46,031 --> 00:37:51,031
所以我任凭它咬我
So I forgive him when he bites me

462
00:37:51,032 --> 00:38:00,041
因为我知道它受过的伤害
because I know what it is like to never feel safe.

463
00:38:00,075 --> 00:38:06,017
都是因为你
And that is because of you.

464
00:38:07,042 --> 00:38:15,019
所以今天...我只问你一件事
So today...I ask only one thing of you.

465
00:38:15,020 --> 00:38:20,014
我要你向我承认
I ask you now that you show me the respect

466
00:38:20,015 --> 00:38:24,093
你对我做的一切...
of acknowledging what you did to me...

467
00:38:24,094 --> 00:38:32,061
是你拷问我 折磨我...
that it was you who questioned me, that tortured me...

468
00:38:32,062 --> 00:38:38,036
你记得我
and that you remember me.

469
00:38:50,065 --> 00:38:55,069
我记得你
I remember you.

470
00:38:56,076 --> 00:39:01,035
我记得你的脸
I remember your face.

471
00:39:01,036 --> 00:39:08,064
你的脸总让我心神不宁
Your face has haunted me ever since I left Iraq.

472
00:39:22,027 --> 00:39:26,021
我很抱歉
I am sorry.

473
00:39:26,022 --> 00:39:32,073
抱歉我对你做的一切
I am so sorry for what I did to you.

474
00:39:41,086 --> 00:39:47,013
我原谅你
I forgive you.

475
00:39:49,005 --> 00:39:57,048
当我丈夫回来后 我会告诉他我犯了一个错误
When my husband returns, I will tell him I made a terrible mistake

476
00:39:57,049 --> 00:40:02,025
那个人不是你...
that it was not you...

477
00:40:02,026 --> 00:40:05,072
然后他会放了你
and he will release you.

478
00:40:05,073 --> 00:40:08,052
为什么?
Why ?

479
00:40:08,053 --> 00:40:11,079
你为什么让我走?
Why are you letting me go?

480
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:19,043
我们都能做到那些孩子对这只猫做的事...
We are all capable of doing what those children did to this cat...

481
00:40:19,044 --> 00:40:21,086
但我不会
but I will not do that.

482
00:40:21,087 --> 00:40:27,031
我不会这样做的
I will not be that.

483
00:40:36,084 --> 00:40:38,071
我们应该杀了他 Sayid
We should kill him, Sayid.

484
00:40:38,072 --> 00:40:44,019
他已经说了他会杀了我们的
He already told us that he would kill us.

485
00:40:47,068 --> 00:40:50,029
不
No

486
00:40:50,030 --> 00:40:52,051
他是我的囚犯
He's my prisoner.

487
00:40:52,052 --> 00:40:57,070
我来决定他的命运
I will decide his fate.

488
00:41:00,035 --> 00:41:03,025
我可以看出这里的东西都没用了
I can see you didn't find anything worth taking.

489
00:41:03,026 --> 00:41:06,004
我又玩了那个愚蠢的象棋游戏
Actually, I just played that silly chess game again

490
00:41:06,005 --> 00:41:12,039
现在我知道你为什么不让我赢它了
and now I realize why you didn't want me to beat it.

491
00:41:12,040 --> 00:41:17,025
那意味着什么?
Meaning what ?

492
00:41:23,038 --> 00:41:25,087
你做了什么 John?
What have you done, John?

493
00:41:25,088 --> 00:41:29,024
那是唯一有希望和外界联系的地方!
That place was our one hope of communication with the outside world!

494
00:41:29,025 --> 00:41:32,040
那电脑说如果我们被"敌人"入侵
The computer said if there was an incursion by the hostiles

495
00:41:32,041 --> 00:41:39,070
我应该输入7-7 所以我就这么做了
I should enter 7-7, so I entered 7-7.

496
00:41:44,034 --> 00:41:46,000
我们应该走了
We should go.

497
00:41:46,001 --> 00:41:52,088
如果周围有人的话 他们会被这里的爆炸吸引过来的
If anyone's around, this explosion is going to attract their attention.

